nt-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ed1i cao \u0111\u00f3 su\u1ed1t g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 nay. Gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng k\u1ef5 r\u01a1 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0!&rdquo; &ndash; D\u00e2n Anh \u0111ang kh\u00e1o nhau n\u1eeda \u0111\u00f9a n\u1eeda th\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n \u1edf c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\" target=\"_blank\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t gieo r\u1eafc qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, d\u00e0n Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1ebb trung \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea5n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp t\u1eebng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 cha anh, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Colombia \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Thuy Dien vs Anh\" title=\"Preview Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u00ean m\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Anh ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau h\u1ecd th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3m x\u00fac ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 y\u00ean l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u00fd tr\u00ed. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t m\u1ed9t Panama qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i, Tam S\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia hay c\u1ea3 Tunisia ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1eb3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng Anh kh\u00e1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i hay Harry Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/du-am-colombia-vs-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\">Harry Kane: G\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh &ldquo;ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh \u0102ng-l\u00ea&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford v\u1eabn x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, nh\u01b0ng sao ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay c\u1ea3 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o Harry Kane \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf World Cup 2018 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Tam S\u01b0 \u0111ang l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham. M\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam S\u01b0 b\u1ecb ki\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa th\u00ec ngu\u1ed3n cung b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n th\u00ec ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, khi phong c\u00e1ch tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch taca-dada truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao trung b\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 77 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 77 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Nhan-dinh-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-21h00-ngay-77-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Colombia tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u1eeda \u1ea3i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho Anh tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u1edf Moscow, nh\u01b0ng theo d\u00f5i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra</span> \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111i, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00e1i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Scandinavia \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n k\u1ef5 r\u01a1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft nh\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng cho Zlatan \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, khoa h\u1ecdc h\u01a1n v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a h\u01a1n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y b\u1eb1ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Anderson ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng pressing t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e2y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp lo\u1ea1i \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 3/4 tr\u1eadn \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u x\u1ee9ng danh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u t\u00e1i l\u1eb7p chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch hi\u1ec3n h\u00e1ch n\u0103m x\u01b0a, t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u0103m 1994 hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n n\u0103m 1958 khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 77) G\u1ecdi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 77) G\u1ecdi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Nhan-dinh-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-(21h00-ngay-77)-Goi-giac-mo-ve-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ch\u1ec9 e s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi tinh hoa c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 h\u1ebft c\u1ea3 ra cho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn Anh t\u1ed1i nay. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i qua ch\u00e2n nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Emil Forsberg, trong khi Ola Toivonen hay Marcus Berg tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd khuy\u1ebft \u0111i m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t \u1edf Samara khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Mikael Lustig b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c khai th\u00e1c. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec thay v\u00ec tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i hay kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n n\u1ebfu Tam S\u01b0 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Nhan-dinh-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-(21h00-ngay-77)-Goi-giac-mo-ve-hinh-anh-2.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau h\u01a1n hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i Zlatan...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 12 n\u0103m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn knock-out \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t mong ng\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c sang trang l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup (th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2/8 tr\u1eadn) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 28 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Italia 90.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Anh th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1/9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c (World Cup v\u00e0 Euro). Hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 2002 v\u00e0 2006 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 24 l\u1ea7n, th\u1eafng 8 h\u00f2a 9 v\u00e0 thua 7. Trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 Euro, Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 6 v\u00e0 thua 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2002 v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng 2006.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup sau 12 n\u0103m, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 24 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh t\u1eebng 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng hai trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi n\u0103m 1966 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (4-4-2): 1. Olsen; 16. Krafth &ndash; 3. Lindelof &ndash; 4. Granqvist &ndash; 6. Augustinsson; 17. Claesson &ndash; 7. Larsson &ndash; 8. Ekdal &ndash; 10. Forsberg; 20. Toivonen &ndash; 9. Berg<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh (3-5-2): 1. Pickford; 2. Walker &ndash; 5. Stones &ndash; 6. Maguire; 12. Trippier &ndash; 20. Alli &ndash; 8. Henderson &ndash; 7. Lingard &ndash; 3. Rose; 9. Kane &ndash; 10. Sterling<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh: Tam S\u01b0 th\u1eafng 1-0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Thuy Dien vs Anh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-(4-4-2-vs-3-5-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"980","checkdouble":"190574"},{"date":"08:56 07/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-thoai-mai-tam-ly-truoc-tran-cau-sinh-tu-voi-u19-indonesia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 7/7.</h2><h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Indonesia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Indonesia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Indonesia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/36639412_226460401412200_5514359247783067648_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vui v\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f9ng U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay 7/7 m\u1edbi c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 6/7, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp ti\u1ebfng c\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Indonesia, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, n\u1ebfu d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trau chu\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Do \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eeb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 Indonesia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb, s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u1edbn. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 19h ng\u00e0y 7/7, tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Gelora Delta.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bongda24h c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dung-truoc-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tuc-gian-voi-hoc-tro-168-190501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-dung-truoc-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tuc-gian-voi-hoc-tro.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dung-truoc-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tuc-gian-voi-hoc-tro-168-190501.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-344-190577.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-344-190577.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nU19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190441.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190441.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-1 U19 L\u00e0o (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm U19 L\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan-168-190139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan-168-190139.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"979","checkdouble":"190579"},{"date":"04:26 07/07","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Kevin de Bruyne n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kevin de Bruyne ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Lukaku d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f2n De Bruyne b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o. C\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Kevin-de-Bruyne-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Bi-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Bruyne v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng x\u1ed9c th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 30, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, Lukaku \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 De Bruyne x\u1eed l\u00fd k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City \u0111em l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Brazil vs B\u1ec9 </span>ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n, 2 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne tin B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne noi ve tran Brazil vs Bi\" title=\"De Bruyne n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, trong 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Brazil \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"978","checkdouble":"190557"},{"date":"04:17 07/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 1-2.</h2><h2>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275411/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n3-5-2 c\u1ee7a Martinez<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eb9p b\u1ecf s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 quen thu\u1ed9c, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 3-5-2 v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Eden Hazard \u2013 Romelu Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 do ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Brazil c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i \u1edf trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Romelu Lukaku g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ea1t ph\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn, khi c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f3c x\u00f9, Kevin De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n tham gia v\u00e0o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Nhung-diem-nhan-tran-dau-Brazil-vs-Bi-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Fernandinho v\u00e0 Marcelo<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Casemiro, Fernandinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho HLV Tite r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Casemiro l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Ngay trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 cho\u2026 \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Marcelo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Fellaini v\u00e0 Lukaku \u2013 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0110T B\u1ec9, khai th\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2 ch\u1ec9 trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Selecao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Thibaut Courtois li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111em v\u1ec1 cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Tite 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Renato Augusto. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda trong hi\u1ec7p 1, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-Brazil-1-2-Bi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Fernandinho v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2>Tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi Kevin De Bruyne<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5 s\u00fang. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, Kevin De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ec9. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Lukaku, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ebb ch\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng cho Alisson b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y, De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 100 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u2013 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0110T B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 9 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110T g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Italia v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006 v\u1edbi 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng De Bruyne d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/de-bruyne.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9: M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a De Bruyne</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2>Xin ch\u00e0o, EURO 2018!<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Brazil, Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c n\u00e0o c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0. 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay (7/7), Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Viking, trong khi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra, Anh, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Nga hay Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp; ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng \u0111ang th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f2n \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Anh/Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nga/Croatia \u2013 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft th\u1ee9 2. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn t\u1ea1i World Cup, l\u00fd do h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/Nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-Brazil-1-2-Bi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn gi\u1eefa 2 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 1-2, t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-brazil-421-190556.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-roberto-martinez-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-brazil-421-190556.html\">HLV Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 1-2. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"977","checkdouble":"190558"},{"date":"05:16 07/07","title":"Thiago Silva \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/thiago-silva-dau-don-sau-that-bai-truoc-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Brazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n an to\u00e0n trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, anh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Du-am-Brazil-vs-Bi-vong-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Coutinho trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay c\u1ee7a Courtois \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 tho\u00e1t thua trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Douglas Costa \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly kh\u00e1 g\u1ea7n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 2, Neymar c\u00f3 c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng \u0111i v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang nh\u01b0ng Courtois v\u1eabn bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang Whoscored ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay v\u00e0 Brazil l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 thua Ph\u00e1p 0-2 qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Selecao nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite mang x\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n danh d\u1ef1 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil thua Bi 1-2\" title=\"Brazil thua Bi 1-2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Brazil v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng Brazil ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 B\u1ec9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0 sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. Brazil \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u lo\u1ea1i trong 4 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (Ph\u00e1p 2006, H\u00e0 Lan 2010, \u0110\u1ee9c 2014 v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 2018).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Brazil th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng \u1edf World Cup 2108. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 thua nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Argentina v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p, Colombia thua Anh c\u00f2n Brazil th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t VCK Euro thu nh\u1ecf. D\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kevin de Bruyne</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, HLV Roberto Martinez s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 v\u1edbi Romelu Lukaku, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 Lukaku l\u1ea1i d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng vai tr\u00f2 trung phong cho De Bruyne.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne noi ve tran Brazil vs Bi\" title=\"De Bruyne n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Martinez khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Brazil b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. V\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, De Bruyne li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Selecao b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng xuy\u00ean th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh. Ph\u00fat 31, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, Lukaku nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 De Bruyne tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span> ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng De Bruyne, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n, 2 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Brazil</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Brazil \u0111\u00e3 tung ra t\u1edbi 29 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, 9 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ef1c th\u1ea5p. Nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar phung phi co hoi\" title=\"Neymar phung phi co hoi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Neymar-phung-phi-co-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i phung ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJesus l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 22 l\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Douglas Costa \u1edf ph\u00fat 57.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 trong nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch duy nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Neymar thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n s\u1ed1 10 b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Eden Hazard. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t&nbsp; trong khi \u0111\u00f3 khi s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Neymar th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i NHM Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Brazil (6 l\u1ea7n), song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Willian hay Firmino c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Fernandinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Casemiro b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 bu\u1ed9c HLV Tite ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Fernandinho ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Fernandinho phan luoi nha\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Fernandinho ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Fernandinho ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat 13, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Chadli, Fernandinho trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra anh ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tr\u00ean thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Fernandinho n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, vi\u1ec7c anh x\u1eed l\u00fd ch\u1eadm sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil, anh kh\u00f4ng tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thay th\u1ebf Casemiro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Romelu Lukaku, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao Tam t\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea tu choi co hoi ket hop De Bruyne, Lukaku va Hazard thanh mot khoi\" title=\"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p De Bruyne, Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p De Bruyne, Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Brazil g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Lukaku l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 De Bruyne n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0, Hazard d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e3y t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t CLB, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"976","checkdouble":"190561"},{"date":"05:15 07/07","title":"\"Noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng\" Neymar, Mbappe su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb t\u1ea9n v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/noi-guong-neymar-mbappe-suyt-nua-bi-tan-vi-hoc-doi-thoi-an-va.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ee3t n\u00e0y, Kylian Mbappe m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh x\u1ea5u. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mbappe \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Uruguay.\r\n</h2><h2>Mbappe h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Neymar th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Raphael Varane v\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m&rdquo; kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe an va tho thien trong tran thang DT Uruguay\" title=\"Mbappe \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/noi-guong-neymar-mbappe-suyt-nua-bi-tan-vi-hoc-doi-thoi-an-va.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Uruguay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o c\u00e1nh tay c\u1ee7a CR7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay (Christian Rodriguez) v\u00e0 l\u0103n ra \u0103n v\u1ea1. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi gian t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, tranh c\u00e3i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5 ra v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Diego Godin l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea9n Mbappe v\u00ec di\u1ec5n tr\u00f2, trong khi Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ee9ng ta b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e0n em v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khi\u00eau kh\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u1ec9 khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ra m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho Mbappe m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i h\u00e3y b\u1ecf qua v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng b\u1eadn t\u00e2m suy ngh\u0129. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1p l\u1eddi v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe an the vang\" title=\"Mbappe \u0103n th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/mbap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0103n th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;HLV lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00f4i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 l\u00f2ng tin \u0111\u00f3. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ng\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 2, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd HLV Deschamps c\u1ea7n c\u1ea5m Mbappe \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n &ldquo;\u0103n \u0111\u00f2n&rdquo; b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-lai-gay-soc-voi-phat-bieu-ac-y-ve-dt-uruguay-421-190553.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/huyen-thoai-mu-lai-gay-soc-voi-phat-bieu-ac-y-ve-dt-uruguay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-lai-gay-soc-voi-phat-bieu-ac-y-ve-dt-uruguay-421-190553.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Uruguay</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 1 v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Luis Suarez v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/phap.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 0-2 Ph\u00e1p (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00e1c xa nh\u1eefng g\u00ec gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dua-phap-vao-ban-ket-griezmann-phat-bieu-day-xuc-dong-421-190545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/dua-phap-vao-ban-ket-griezmann-phat-bieu-day-xuc-dong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dua-phap-vao-ban-ket-griezmann-phat-bieu-day-xuc-dong-421-190545.html\">\u0110\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng</span><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 anh c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"975","checkdouble":"190562"},{"date":"06:15 07/07","title":"HLV Brazil l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9. HLV 57 tu\u1ed5i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Selecao t\u1edbi t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Brazil tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn, l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Selecao \u0111\u00e3 rung l\u00ean sau pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Fernandinho ph\u00fat 13.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Brazil c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9. Kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda sau c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, Kevin De Bruyne v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u201cn\u00e3 ph\u00e1o\u201d ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/HLV-Tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Brazil-1-2-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Brazil l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Renato Augusto. H\u1ecd thua chung cu\u1ed9c 1-2 v\u00e0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Tite l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 26 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, 8 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch song ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite\" title=\"HLV Tite\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn. \u201cNh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u00edch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n ni\u1ec1m vui. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 C\u0110V trung l\u1eadp, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-brazil-421-190556.html\">HLV Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-bi-463-190541.html\">Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9: H\u1ea1 knock-out Selecao, B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1eb9n G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"974","checkdouble":"190564"},{"date":"06:14 07/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Brazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n an to\u00e0n trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, anh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Du-am-Brazil-vs-Bi-vong-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Coutinho trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay c\u1ee7a Courtois \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 tho\u00e1t thua trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Douglas Costa \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly kh\u00e1 g\u1ea7n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 2, Neymar c\u00f3 c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng \u0111i v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang nh\u01b0ng Courtois v\u1eabn bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang Whoscored ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay v\u00e0 Brazil l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 thua Ph\u00e1p 0-2 qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Selecao nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite mang x\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n danh d\u1ef1 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil thua Bi 1-2\" title=\"Brazil thua Bi 1-2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Brazil v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng Brazil ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 B\u1ec9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0 sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. Brazil \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u lo\u1ea1i trong 4 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (Ph\u00e1p 2006, H\u00e0 Lan 2010, \u0110\u1ee9c 2014 v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 2018).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Brazil th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng \u1edf World Cup 2108. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 thua nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Argentina v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p, Colombia thua Anh c\u00f2n Brazil th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t VCK Euro thu nh\u1ecf. D\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kevin de Bruyne</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, HLV Roberto Martinez s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 v\u1edbi Romelu Lukaku, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 Lukaku l\u1ea1i d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng vai tr\u00f2 trung phong cho De Bruyne.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne noi ve tran Brazil vs Bi\" title=\"De Bruyne n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Martinez khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Brazil b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. V\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, De Bruyne li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Selecao b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng xuy\u00ean th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh. Ph\u00fat 31, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, Lukaku nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 De Bruyne tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span> ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng De Bruyne, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n, 2 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Brazil</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Brazil \u0111\u00e3 tung ra t\u1edbi 29 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, 9 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ef1c th\u1ea5p. Nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar phung phi co hoi\" title=\"Neymar phung phi co hoi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Neymar-phung-phi-co-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i phung ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJesus l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 22 l\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Douglas Costa \u1edf ph\u00fat 57.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 trong nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch duy nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Neymar thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n s\u1ed1 10 b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Eden Hazard. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t&nbsp; trong khi \u0111\u00f3 khi s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Neymar th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i NHM Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Brazil (6 l\u1ea7n), song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Willian hay Firmino c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Fernandinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Casemiro b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 bu\u1ed9c HLV Tite ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Fernandinho ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Fernandinho phan luoi nha\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Fernandinho ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Fernandinho ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat 13, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Chadli, Fernandinho trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra anh ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tr\u00ean thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Fernandinho n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, vi\u1ec7c anh x\u1eed l\u00fd ch\u1eadm sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil, anh kh\u00f4ng tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thay th\u1ebf Casemiro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Romelu Lukaku, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao Tam t\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea tu choi co hoi ket hop De Bruyne, Lukaku va Hazard thanh mot khoi\" title=\"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p De Bruyne, Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p De Bruyne, Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Brazil g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Lukaku l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 De Bruyne n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0, Hazard d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e3y t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t CLB, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"973","checkdouble":"190565"},{"date":"06:30 07/07","title":"Cavani n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/cavani-noi-gi-sau-khi-khong-the-gop-mat-cung-dong-doi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Edinson Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Cavani chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2>Cavani ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, khi ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edinson Cavani \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c anh v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 t\u1ecf ra t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Uruguay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2, c\u00f2n Cavani ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 v\u1ebb th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cavani chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/cavani-noi-gi-sau-khi-khong-the-gop-mat-cung-dong-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. Anh vi\u1ebft: \u201cBu\u1ed3n? R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng \u0110T Uruguay \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, \u1edf c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Uruguay, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00f4m nay. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. H\u00e3y ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. Ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean Uruguay, cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Cavani l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Oscar Tabarez. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng anh l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1eefa Brazil vs B\u1ec9 \u2013 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n duy nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn tham chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/noi-guong-neymar-mbappe-suyt-nua-bi-tan-vi-hoc-doi-thoi-an-va-421-190562.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/noi-guong-neymar-mbappe-suyt-nua-bi-tan-vi-hoc-doi-thoi-an-va.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/noi-guong-neymar-mbappe-suyt-nua-bi-tan-vi-hoc-doi-thoi-an-va-421-190562.html\">Noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng Neymar, Mbappe su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb t\u1ea9n v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ee3t n\u00e0y, Kylian Mbappe m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh x\u1ea5u. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mbappe \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-lai-gay-soc-voi-phat-bieu-ac-y-ve-dt-uruguay-421-190553.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/huyen-thoai-mu-lai-gay-soc-voi-phat-bieu-ac-y-ve-dt-uruguay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-lai-gay-soc-voi-phat-bieu-ac-y-ve-dt-uruguay-421-190553.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Uruguay</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 1 v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Luis Suarez v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/phap.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 0-2 Ph\u00e1p (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00e1c xa nh\u1eefng g\u00ec gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"972","checkdouble":"190566"},{"date":"06:39 07/07","title":"Ronaldo k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Brazil ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Tite","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/ronaldo-phat-bieu-ve-tite.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Tite. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh\u201d hy v\u1ecdng \u0110T Brazil s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Tite b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Selecao \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n thua ch\u1ec9 sau 31 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Fernandinho v\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa s\u1ea5m s\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Kevin De Bruyne. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 76, Renato Augusto m\u1edbi g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 1 b\u00e0n cho Brazil, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Trong ng\u00e0y Neymar ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, Selecao thua chung cu\u1ed9c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Tite v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Tite v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Ronaldo-phat-bieu-ve-HLV-Tite-va-hy-vong-ong-o-lai-DT-Brazil-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Brazil sau 27 tr\u1eadn d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tite. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Tite</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, Tite ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u1ee3i \u00fd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Tite v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m cho Selecao, c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite cua Brazil\" title=\"HLV Tite cua Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/ronaldo-phat-bieu-ve-tite.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Tite v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft trong 2 k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1eeba qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Selecao, lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i t\u1ec7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Tite s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111ang c\u00f2n dang d\u1edf.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi-421-190557.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Kevin de Bruyne n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-brazil-421-190556.html\">HLV Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-bi-463-190541.html\">Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9: H\u1ea1 knock-out Selecao, B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1eb9n G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"971","checkdouble":"190567"},{"date":"06:52 07/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh, Ibra bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Beckham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-ibra-buong-loi-thach-thuc-hai-huoc-voi-beckham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 36 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ibra \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng khai tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Ibra th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Beckham<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Ibrahimovic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ibra tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u1ecfi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span>. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1981 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn&rdquo; c\u00f9ng Beckham &ndash; th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Yo, Beckham th\u00e2n m\u1ebfn, n\u1ebfu \u0110T Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua cho anh b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng, anh ph\u1ea3i t\u1eb7ng t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec t\u1ea1i IKEA (m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p), OK ch\u1ee9?&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ee9ng nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Ch\u1ec9 5 ti\u1ebfng sau b\u00e0i post, b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a Ibra \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1,6 tri\u1ec7u like v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u comment, trong \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tag t\u00ean Beckham v\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibra \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham\" title=\"Ibra \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/ibr.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i trong b\u00e0i post Ibra \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: &ldquo;OK th\u00f4i, <strong>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng th\u00ec ch\u00fa mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</strong> Anh s\u1ebd mua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec t\u1ea1i IKEA cho c\u0103n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fa \u1edf Los Angeles. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, anh mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ebfn SV\u0110 Wembley \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3, m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 \u0103n khoai t\u00e2y chi\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, khi c\u1ea3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a&hellip; SV\u0110 Wembley c\u0169ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. &ldquo;\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo; n\u00e0y b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: &ldquo;Beckham, anh c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eb7ng anh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ibra kh\u00f4ng? S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 hay s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u00f9y th\u00edch!&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1ee5 c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c vui v\u1ebb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate \u0111ang chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Li\u1ec7u v\u1ee5 Ibra \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham s\u1ebd c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ra sao, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vardy-dinh-chan-thuong-nhieu-kha-nang-lo-tu-ket-421-190522.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/vardy-dinh-chan-thuong-nhieu-kha-nang-lo-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vardy-dinh-chan-thuong-nhieu-kha-nang-lo-tu-ket-421-190522.html\">\u0110T Anh thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nJamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\">Ibrahimovic: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m n\u00edn</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Zlatan Ibrahimovic cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"970","checkdouble":"190568"}]}